{"tid":659194,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中興：積極與美國政府溝通調整或取消激活拒絕令","createTime":"2018-05-09T15:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T16:12:21.000Z","uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"48d94a57167ff971c49127f21d074f31b0d5cdf3","tid":659194,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T15:10:38.000Z","msg":"香港電台-財經<br />\n<br />\n中興通訊發公告指，目前現金充足，在合法合規的前提下，堅守商業信用。公司積極與美國政府相關部門溝通，推動對方調整或取消激活拒絕令，推動事情向好方向發展。<br />\n<br />\n中興說，受到美國商務部工業與安全局(BIS)簽發的激活拒絕令影響，已無法進行主要經營活動。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/中興-積極與美國政府溝通調整或取消激活拒絕令-121254949.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Ffinance%2F%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%88-%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%BA%9D%E9%80%9A%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E6%88%96%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E6%BF%80%E6%B4%BB%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E4%BB%A4-121254949.html&d=nSV7y%2FYQHtUxJ1LV2LfN8cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=46fb932c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/中興-積極與美國政府溝通調整或取消激活拒絕令-121254949.html</a>"},{"pid":"b01b7b4c21f763c2d24a525d8f33cca7edd86581","tid":659194,"uid":158613,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T15:18:45.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢叫做激活拒絕令"},{"pid":"29d4b94596864acfc90e3c4eff9d36be7845b905","tid":659194,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"全力篤死華為?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcce2a48be7a0ed06c8ad4bdd5de9535d06ad2b","tid":659194,"uid":23682,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b01b7b4c21f763c2d24a525d8f33cca7edd86581","tid":659194,"uid":158613,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T15:18:45.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢叫做激活拒絕令"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T15:32:39.000Z","msg":"Deactivate ban?<br />\n明顯係 Google translate易<br />\n中国又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac